# Euclid Insights - AI Agent Instructions

You are working on Euclid Insights, a thought leadership blog for Euclid Innovations. Read CLAUDE.md for the complete reference guide. Key rules summarized here:

## Writing Style (Google Developer Documentation Style)
- Sentence-case headings: "The business case for cloud"
- Second person: "you/your" — not "organizations" abstractly
- Active voice, present tense
- Cut filler words (actually, basically, simply)
- Bold for key term introduction only

## Brand Colors (Tailwind)
- Primary: euclid-teal (#0AB3B3), euclid-navy (#273171)
- Dark: euclid-teal-dark (#014745), euclid-gray-dark (#2D2D2D)
- Light: euclid-cyan (#D3FFFE), euclid-gray-light (#F7F8FA)
- Accent: euclid-green (#61CE70)

## Fonts
- Headings/nav: Poppins (font-poppins)
- Body: Roboto (font-roboto)
- Blockquotes: Roboto Slab (font-roboto-slab)

## Cover Images
- Flat geometric monochromatic SVG illustrations with grain texture
- 800x450 viewBox, single hue per article, stored in public/images/covers/
- Used colors: purple, green, red, blue, orange

## Stock Images
- Download from Unsplash/Pexels, store locally in public/images/articles/
- Never hotlink external images
- Use: `<img src="/images/articles/name.jpg" alt="..." class="rounded-2xl my-10 w-full" />`

## Logos
- Header navbar: Logo-Icon-Transparent-BG.png (original)
- Footer/favicon/structured data: cropped-Logo-Icon-Transparent-shadow.png

## Dark Sections in Articles
- Always add `not-prose` class to dark-background containers in MDX
- Without it, prose styles override text to dark gray

## Tech Stack
- Astro (hybrid SSR) + @astrojs/node adapter
- Tailwind CSS, MDX content collections
- Microsoft SSO (process.env, not import.meta.env)
- PM2 + Nginx on Azure VM
- GitHub Actions CI/CD on push to master
